{
  "id": "adv_event_2601_01_01",
  "title": "ⅢX公式動画\nチャンネル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――12月27日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.4200000048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、間違っていたのかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666665872,
      "endTime": 6.2585713704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルグループは、仲がいい方が好感度が高いから\n私達も、対外的にはそのように見せてきたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4652379513,
      "endTime": 14.414716386799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.6147161961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか……私達の素を、表に出すつもりなの？\nお互い大嫌いだけど、仕方なく一緒にいるだけだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6147161961,
      "endTime": 25.3147158146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.5080490907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "……マジかよ\nよりにもよってあんたが、そんなこと言い出すとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5080490907,
      "endTime": 31.1444209894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.3510877133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。私は本気よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3510877133,
      "endTime": 33.9510876656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四ヶ月前、8月1日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7510876656,
      "endTime": 36.0510869026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "打倒BIG4作戦会議",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0577541079,
      "endTime": 37.0977576653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.0977576653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "えー、それでは。月ストとサニピとリズノワと……\nBIG4のやつらをどうぶっ潰すかの会議を始めまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0310924928,
      "endTime": 46.4145389956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.6278720618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "こころがいっつもマウント取ってきて、ウザいのよ\nここらで一発、どっちが上か思い知らせてやんないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6278720618,
      "endTime": 53.9878720046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "私怨は捨て置いても、VENUSグランプリに向けて\n作戦を練っていく必要はあるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1745387476,
      "endTime": 59.901772443700004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.1084390721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……今度こそ、長瀬麻奈を超えるためにも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1084390721,
      "endTime": 63.6130649171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.819731498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ私怨なんじゃ……ま、私のブランドの宣伝でも\n『トップアイドルがデザインした服』って言いたいしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.819731498,
      "endTime": 73.339731765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは……やりたいこと見つかったら辞める、とか\n言ってたけど、まだ続けんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.539731765,
      "endTime": 79.5345617059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.539731765
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.7412283344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "誰かさんと違って、kanaは立派な大人だから\n仕事を途中でほっぽりだしたりしないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7412283344,
      "endTime": 86.67281583970001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "それは何よりね。……それで、話を本題に戻して\n私達がBIG4に返り咲くための戦略の話をしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8728159351,
      "endTime": 97.8728157444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.8728159351
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.7333366394
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.0594824873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "まず、敵の状況を整理するわ。星見の他の子達は\n親しみやすさを強調する方針で、BIG4に登り詰めた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0594824873,
      "endTime": 106.5230652891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーが、等身大の魅力がどうとかうるさいしね\nあいつは、kana達にもそうさせたいみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7097320321,
      "endTime": 115.8980310204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.7097320321
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.1046975536
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "他のお子様達はともかく、私達の素なんて表に出したら\n炎上しかしないって、いい加減気付いてほしいわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1046975536,
      "endTime": 124.89236177629999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "それに私、そういうチープ路線嫌いだし\n結局そんなの、パッとしないやつらの言い訳じゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0990283094,
      "endTime": 133.18635273799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.0990283094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "Miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "とは言え……星見の他の子はそれで結果を出している\nだとするなら、否定しきれるものでもないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3996860905,
      "endTime": 142.45544532969998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.3996860905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに。なら、kana達はもっとうまくやって\nあいつらのファンを、根こそぎ奪ってやろうじゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.655445139,
      "endTime": 150.9250143452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.655445139
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.4000033061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……\nそういうことなら、まぁいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1250141545,
      "endTime": 156.76156629759998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 151.1250141545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "そういや、{user}が\nスリクスの公式チャンネル作りたいとか言ってたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9682328784,
      "endTime": 162.1882329547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.9682328784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2601_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "そこでkana達のオフとか、素……っぽいところも\n動画にして、配信してみるって感じかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
